<!--
Conformance vector: SEPA SCT Inst pacs.008.001.08 outbound credit
transfer for RT1 / TIPS submission.

Verified scheme rules per EPC SCT Inst Interbank Implementation Guide
2019 v1.0 and TIPS UDFS:

- Document namespace: urn:iso:std:iso:20022:tech:xsd:pacs.008.001.08
- NbOfTxs = 1 (RT1 / TIPS reject bulk pacs.008 - single tx only)
- SttlmInf.SttlmMtd = CLRG (mandatory for RT1; TIPS accepts CLRG or INGA)
- LclInstrm.Cd = INST (MANDATORY — this is what makes it SCT Inst)
- SvcLvl.Cd = SEPA (mandatory)
- ChrgBr = SLEV (only allowed value in SCT Inst)
- Currency = EUR (only allowed)
- Agents identified by BICFI (not ClrSysMmbId)
- Accounts identified by IBAN (not Othr/Id)
- UETR present, lowercase hyphenated UUID v4
-->
<Document xmlns="urn:iso:std:iso:20022:tech:xsd:pacs.008.001.08">
